<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MOOCs Document Verification</title>
    <style>
        /* Inline CSS */
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .logo {
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
            max-width: 100px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #007bff;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #444;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        h3 {
            color: #4CAF50;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        p {
            color: #444;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-align: justify;
        }
        .footer {
            color: #777;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        /* Media Query for Mobile View */
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            h2 {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
            h3 {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
            p {
                font-size: 14px;
            }
            .footer {
                font-size: 12px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dd1rpkqom/image/upload/v1713812782/Logo/htufx0pzpqdah3v1mkqw.png" alt="HIT" class="logo">
        <h1>Haldia Institute of Technology</h1>
        <h2>Department of Computer Science and Engineering - Data Science</h2>
        <h3>Congratulations!</h3>
        <p>Hello <%= user %>,</p>
        <p>We are thrilled to inform you that your MOOCs document titled "<%= moocsTitle %>" has been successfully verified by the administrator.</p>
        <p>This verification marks a significant milestone in your academic journey, showcasing your dedication to continuous learning and skill development.</p>
        <p>Your verified document will be added to your academic record, further enhancing your credentials.</p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact us. We're here to support you.</p>
        <p class="footer">Best regards,<br>Mr. Soumya Mukherjee,<br>Head of Department, Department of Computer Science Engineering (Data Science)</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
